BAU Profitable Capacity for Cost Effectiveness Additions for Hybrid Power Plants[Hybrid Electricity Source\
		,Optimization Pass,RPS]=
	IF THEN ELSE(
	  BAU Profitable Capacity as Share of Existing Capacity for Cost Effectiveness Additions for Hybrid Power Plants\
		[Hybrid Electricity Source
	,Optimization Pass,RPS] = :NA:,
	
	  0,
	
	  MAX(0,BAU Profitable Capacity as Share of Existing Capacity for Cost Effectiveness Additions for Hybrid Power Plants\
		[Hybrid Electricity Source,Optimization Pass,RPS]
	    * MAX(
	        BAU Minimum Buildable Capacity for Plants,
	        BAU Last Year Electricity Generation Capacity[Hybrid Electricity Source]
	      )
	    -BAU Profitable Capacity for Cost Effectiveness Additions[Hybrid Electricity Source\
		,Optimization Pass,RPS]
	  )
	) ~~|
BAU Profitable Capacity for Cost Effectiveness Additions for Hybrid Power Plants[Hybrid Electricity Source\
