BAU Profitable Capacity for Seasonal Dispatchable Clean Reliability Additions[Clean Dispatchable Electricity Source\
		,Optimization Pass]=
	IF THEN ELSE(
	 IF THEN ELSE(
	  MAX(0,
	  BAU Total Energy Market and Capacity Market Revenue for Seasonal Clean Dispatchable Reliability\
		[Clean Dispatchable Electricity Source,Optimization Pass]
	
	  -(
	     BAU Annualized Fixed Costs per Unit New Capacity[Clean Dispatchable Electricity Source\
		]
	     * SoCtMbCtbDP Share of Costs that Must be Covered to Be Deemed Profitable[Clean Dispatchable Electricity Source\
		]
	  )
	) <= 0,
	
	  0,
	
	  LOOKUP INVERT(
	    CSCCCMvSoECBtY Capacity Cost Multiplier vs Share of Existing Capacity Built This Year\
		[summer],
	    MAX(0,
	  BAU Total Energy Market and Capacity Market Revenue for Seasonal Clean Dispatchable Reliability\
		[Clean Dispatchable Electricity Source,Optimization Pass]
	
	  -(
	    BAU Annualized Fixed Costs per Unit New Capacity[Clean Dispatchable Electricity Source\
		]
	     * SoCtMbCtbDP Share of Costs that Must be Covered to Be Deemed Profitable[Clean Dispatchable Electricity Source\
		]
	  )
	)
	  )
	)
	= :NA:,
	
	  0,
	
	 IF THEN ELSE(
	  MAX(0,
	  BAU Total Energy Market and Capacity Market Revenue for Seasonal Clean Dispatchable Reliability\
		[Clean Dispatchable Electricity Source,Optimization Pass]
	
	  -(
	     BAU Annualized Fixed Costs per Unit New Capacity[Clean Dispatchable Electricity Source\
		]
	     * SoCtMbCtbDP Share of Costs that Must be Covered to Be Deemed Profitable[Clean Dispatchable Electricity Source\
		]
	  )
	) <= 0,
	
	  0,
	
	  LOOKUP INVERT(
	    CSCCCMvSoECBtY Capacity Cost Multiplier vs Share of Existing Capacity Built This Year\
		[summer],
	    MAX(0,
	  BAU Total Energy Market and Capacity Market Revenue for Seasonal Clean Dispatchable Reliability\
		[Clean Dispatchable Electricity Source,Optimization Pass]
	
	  -(
	    BAU Annualized Fixed Costs per Unit New Capacity[Clean Dispatchable Electricity Source\
		]
	     * SoCtMbCtbDP Share of Costs that Must be Covered to Be Deemed Profitable[Clean Dispatchable Electricity Source\
		]
	  )
	)
	  )
	)
	
	  * MAX(
	      BAU Minimum Buildable Capacity for Plants,
	      BAU Last Year Electricity Generation Capacity[Clean Dispatchable Electricity Source\
		]
	    )
	)
	~	MW
	~	If we do not test for :NA: (no number), then an out-of-bounds lookup in \
		the prior variable can produce a large random number here, which can throw \
		off the model. It may be better to output zero for an out-of-bounds lookup.
	|

BAU Profitable Capacity for Seasonal Dispatchable Clean Reliability CCUS Retrofits[Clean Dispatchable Electricity Source
,Optimization Pass]=
