Boolean Is Industry the Recipient of Funds by Policy[Industry Process Emissions Policy\
		]=
	1,	{methane capture}
	1,	{methane destruction}
	1,	{f-gas substitution}
	1,	{f-gas destruction}
	1,	{f-gas recovery}
	0,	{f-gas inspct maint retrofit}
	0,	{cropland and rice measures}
	1,	{livestock measures}
	0,	{tillage}
	1,	{cement measures}
	1	{N2O abatement}
	~	Dmnl
	~	This is part of the way these industrial policies are assumed to work in \
		the model (part of the definitions of the blue user-specified policies), \
		so no external source is needed. It defines whether funds are paid to \
		industry (e.g., to upgrade technology) or to people (e.g., to perform \
		maintenance).
	|

