Change in Cash Flow by Entity From IO Outputs[Cash Flow Entity] :EXCEPT:   [government\
		],[labor and consumers]=
	Direct Change in Cash Flow by Entity[Cash Flow Entity] ~~|
Change in Cash Flow by Entity From IO Outputs[government]=
	Direct Change in Cash Flow by Entity[government]
	
	+ IF THEN ELSE(
	    BDMFL Boolean Disable Macroeconomic Feedback Loops = 0,
	
	    SUM(Last Year Change in Domestic Individual Income Tax Revenue by ISIC Code[ISIC Code\
		!]),
	
	    0
	) ~~|
Change in Cash Flow by Entity From IO Outputs[labor and consumers]=
	Direct Change in Cash Flow by Entity[labor and consumers]
	
	+ IF THEN ELSE(
	    BDMFL Boolean Disable Macroeconomic Feedback Loops = 0,
	
	    Last Year Change in Labor and Consumers Earnings After Income Taxes,
	
	    0
	)
	~	$
	~		|

Change in CCS New Capital Eqpt Cost by Hydrogen Sector=
