	- BAU CCS Subsidy Amount Paid to Hydrogen Sector
	~	$
	~		|

Change in CES Costs=
	This Year Ongoing CES Costs-BAU This Year Ongoing CES Costs
	~	$
	~		~	:SUPPLEMENTARY 
	|

Change in Compensation per Domestic Employee=
	Weighted Average Compensation per Employee
	- BAU Weighted Average Compensation per Employee
	~	$/job
	~		|

Change in Compensation per Domestic Employee by ISIC Code[ISIC Code]=
	Compensation per Employee by ISIC Code[ISIC Code]
	- BAU Compensation per Employee by ISIC Code[ISIC Code]
	~	$/job
	~		~	:SUPPLEMENTARY 
	|

