Cost of Capacity Construction before Construction Subsidies[Electricity Source]=
	New Generation Capacity Excluding Retrofit Capacity[Electricity Source]
	* Construction Cost per Unit Capacity before Construction Subsidies[Electricity Source\
		]
	
	+ New Hybrid Grid Battery Storage Capacity[Electricity Source]
	* Total Battery Cost per Unit Capacity
	~	$
	~		|

Cost of Capacity Retrofitting before Construction Subsidies[Electricity Source]=
