	SUM(
	  Reduction Achieved by Marginal Cost[other metals inspct maint retrofit,Marginal Abatement Cost\
		!]
	  * PERAC Marginal Cost Definitions[Marginal Abatement Cost!]
	  / Grams per Metric Ton CO2e
	)
	
	- Change in Cost to Industry from Non BAU Process Emissions Additions[other metals 242\
		,indst f gas inspct maint retrofit] ~~|
Cost of Process Emissions Policies[chemicals 20,indst N2O abatement]=
	SUM(
	  Reduction Achieved by Marginal Cost[chemicals N2O abatement,Marginal Abatement Cost\
		!]
	  * PERAC Marginal Cost Definitions[Marginal Abatement Cost!]
	  / Grams per Metric Ton CO2e
	)
	
	- Change in Cost to Industry from Non BAU Process Emissions Additions[chemicals 20,indst N2O abatement\
		]
	~	$
	~	R&D reduces compliance costs only in cases when the main expense for \
		compliance is to buy equipment, rather than pay workers.
	|

