	   'InputData/trans/EoDfVUwFC/EoDfVUwFC.csv',
	   ',',
	   'B2*'
	)
	~	Dmnl
	~	This variable is also known as the "Fuel Economy Rebound Effect" or "Fuel \
		Cost Rebound Effect."  It is the change in VMT as a fraction of the change \
		in fuel cost.  E.g. for a 1% increase in fuel cost per mile, VMT changes \
		by -0.1%.
