	  Fraction of New Bldg Components Shifted to Other Fuels[Building Component,Building Type\
		]
	  * VECTOR ELM MAP(
	      Selected Policy Implementation Schedule[bldgs new component fuel shifting X heating X urban residential\
		],
	
	      (Building Component-1)*ELMCOUNT(Building Type) + (Building Type-1)
	    )
	)
	~	Dmnl
