		,Emissions Type!]  
	  * Last Year Pollutants Sequestered by Industry Sector[Industry Category,CO2,Emissions Type\
		!]
	)
	  * (1 - RnD CCS Fuel Use Perc Reduction This Year)
	~	BTU
	~		|

