Government Contribution to Change in Domestic Output by ISIC Code[ISIC Code]=
	Government Contribution to Change in Global Output by ISIC Code[ISIC Code]
	* Domestic Content Share of Consumption by ISIC Code[ISIC Code]
	~	$
	~		|

Government Contribution to Change in Global Output by ISIC Code[ISIC Code]=
	Government Revenue Change Allocated by Mechanism[regular spending]
	* Percent of Government Expenditures by ISIC Code[ISIC Code]
	~	$
	~		|

Government Expenditures by ISIC Code by Year[ISIC Code]=
	GaHEbIC Government Expenditures by ISIC Code[ISIC Code]
	* (1 + BAU Percent Change in Output by ISIC Code Using Endogenous Energy Revenues[ISIC Code\
		])
	~	$
	~		|

