Output Energy Related CO2 Emissions from Hard Coal and Lignite=
	(Energy Related Pollutant Emissions by Fuel[CO2,hard coal]
	  + Energy Related Pollutant Emissions by Fuel[CO2,lignite]
	)
	/ MOU Grams per Large Mass Output Unit Pollutant
	~	mass output unit
	~		~	:SUPPLEMENTARY 
