	  + Energy Related Pollutant Emissions by Fuel[CO2,jet fuel or kerosene]
	  + Energy Related Pollutant Emissions by Fuel[CO2,heavy or residual fuel oil]
	  + Energy Related Pollutant Emissions by Fuel[CO2,LPG propane or butane]
	)
	/ MOU Grams per Large Mass Output Unit Pollutant
	~	mass output unit
	~		~	:SUPPLEMENTARY 
