		[Industry Category,Industrial Fuel,
	Industrial Process]
	* Output from New Industrial Equipment[Industry Category,Industrial Process]
	~	$
	~		|

Output from New Industrial Equipment by Industry Category[Industry Category]=
	SUM(Output from New Industrial Equipment[Industry Category,Industrial Process!])
	~	$
	~		|

Output from Preexisting Industrial Equipment[Industry Category,Industrial Process]=
