Percent Animal Products Shifted to Nonanimal Products=
	0
	~	Dmnl [0,1]
	~		|

Percent Animal Products Shifted to Nonanimal Products This Year=
	Percent Animal Products Shifted to Nonanimal Products
	* Selected Policy Implementation Schedule[indst shift to nonanimal products X]
