		] :EXCEPT: [Industry Category ISIC Code],[Fossil and Energy Utility ISIC Code]=
	0 ~~|
Percent of Nonenergy Industry Electricity and Natural Gas Spending by ISIC Code[Industry Category ISIC Code\
		] :EXCEPT: [Fossil and Energy Utility ISIC Code]=
