	~	Dmnl [0,3]
	~	This variable specifies a tightening of BAU fuel economy standards, above \
		and beyond their improvement in the BAU case over the course of the model \
		run.  A value of zero means no improvement beyond the BAU case.  A value \
		of "1" means 100% improvement, or a doubling of the standard (e.g. going \
		from X miles per gallon in 2030 to 2X miles per gallon in 2030).
	|

