		,Marginal Abatement Cost] :EXCEPT:           [cement industry measures,Marginal Abatement Cost\
		],[ngp production methane capture,Marginal Abatement Cost
],[ngp production methane destruction,Marginal Abatement Cost],[ngp processing TnD methane capture\
		,Marginal Abatement Cost
],[ngp processing TnD methane destruction,Marginal Abatement Cost],[chemicals f gas substitution\
		,Marginal Abatement Cost
],[chemicals f gas destruction,Marginal Abatement Cost],[chemicals f gas recovery,Marginal Abatement Cost\
		],[chemicals inspct maint retrofit
,Marginal Abatement Cost],[coal mining methane capture,Marginal Abatement Cost],[coal mining methane destruction\
		,Marginal Abatement Cost
],[waste management methane capture,Marginal Abatement Cost],[waste management methane destruction\
