Proportion of Primary Energy from Non Fossil Sources=
	Non Fossil Primary Energy
	/
	(
	  Total Primary Energy Use[hard coal]
	  + Total Primary Energy Use[natural gas]
	  + Total Primary Energy Use[nuclear]
	  + Total Primary Energy Use[hydro]
	  + Total Primary Energy Use[wind]
	  + Total Primary Energy Use[solar]
	  + Total Primary Energy Use[biomass]
	  + Total Primary Energy Use[petroleum gasoline]
	  + Total Primary Energy Use[petroleum diesel]
	  + Total Primary Energy Use[biofuel gasoline]
	  + Total Primary Energy Use[biofuel diesel]
	  + Total Primary Energy Use[jet fuel or kerosene]
	  + Total Primary Energy Use[geothermal]
	)
	~	Dmnl
	~	We can't sum across the All Fuels subscript because that would include \
		electricity and heat, energy carriers for which no value exists in the \
		"Total Primary Energy Use" variable.
	~	:SUPPLEMENTARY 
	|

