This Year Demand Response Capacity=
	DRC BAU Demand Response Capacity
	+ (DRC Potential Additional Demand Response Capacity
	   * Fraction of Additional Demand Response Potential Achieved This Year)
	+ Demand Responsive Electricity Capacity for Electrolyzers
	~	MW
	~		|

